description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to appoint a dynamic and dedicated Band 5 Operating Department Practitioner/Anaesthetic nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We work across a wide range of specialties and are keen to promote a multi-skilled workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally you will need to be an experienced Operating Department Practitioner/Anaesthetic Nurse with demonstrable commitment to your own professional development however; full training and support can be given to newly qualified practitioners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Anaesthetic Practitioners work a rotating shift pattern and participate in the On-Call Roster. It is important to us to support our staffs continued professional development and opportunities are available for both in-house and external training and development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Natalie Peters, Principal ODP&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;natalie.peters@hhft.nhs.uk / 01962 825502&lt;/p&gt;
